# Tadawul Fast Bridge — Git Ignore Rules (v2.1.0)
# =============================================================================
# PROD-SAFE EXCLUSION LIST (Hardened + Render/GitHub Friendly)
# Prevent secrets, local envs, caches, build outputs, and runtime artifacts
# from being committed.
#
# Principles
# - Track templates (e.g., .env.example) but never real secrets
# - Prefer narrow ignores over broad ignores
# - Keep .github/ tracked
# - Keep core source tracked (core/, routes/, scripts/, tests/, schemas/)
#
# Version notes (v2.1.0)
# - ✅ Hardened secret patterns (Google SA, OAuth, tokens, PEM/PFX, SSH keys)
# - ✅ Added common local/CI artifacts (ruff/uv, poetry/pdm, pytest, coverage)
# - ✅ Added Render-specific runtime artifacts + local overrides
# - ✅ Added Jupyter + data science artifacts (without ignoring real source)
# - ✅ Safe JSON rules: do NOT ignore all JSON globally (only secret JSON names)
# =============================================================================

